    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) satisfy pre-specified acceptance bounds. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted given the medium model risk level, the regulatory primacy of the F1717 single-condition test, and the corroborating agreement between FEA and experimental results. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion and acceptance of the FEA model for the stated COU.",
